{
  "id": "RAW_7d37370a",
  "title": "挑战 WorldLabs：Visionary，一个全面超越 Marble 底层渲染器的 WebGPU 渲染平台",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651008265&idx=4&sn=0d30fe6ed18cc5146e06d6872b3b6870",
  "date": "2025-12-21 04:19:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">该工作由上海人工智能实验室钟志航团队联合四川大学、东京大学、上海交通大学、西北工业大学共同完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"5\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在李飞飞团队 WorldLabs 推出 Marble、引爆「世界模型（World Model）」热潮之后，一个现实问题逐渐浮出水面：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">世界模型的可视化与交互，依然严重受限于底层 Web 端渲染能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Marble 所依赖的</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于 WebGL 的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;3D Gaussian Splatting (3DGS) 渲染器 SparkJS，让世界模型首次在浏览器中「跑起来」，但也暴露出明显瓶颈：大场景以及复杂场景下，CPU 排序成为性能天花板，动态场景与生成模型难以接入。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">近日，开源项目</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;Visionary&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">给出了一个截然不同的答案：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">基于 WebGPU 与 ONNX，在浏览器中实现真正的动态 3DGS / 4DGS 实时渲染，并在多项测试中全面超越 SparkJS。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524326\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f9e0db4a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibMWHN2gz8SLUucnTjmv5Aogia256TOnRWJiatn5icR39CWqb1YHe0wfMEibzqtkibAJL5x4ib5zgVsLTbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文标题：Visionar y: The World Model Carrier Built on WebGPU-Powered Gaussian Splatting Platform</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">技术报告：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.08478\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.08478</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/Visionary-Laboratory/visionary\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Visionary-Laboratory/visionary</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">在线 Editor：<a href=\"https://visionary-laboratory.github.io/visionary/index_visionary.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://visionary-laboratory.github.io/visionary/index_visionary.html</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"10\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">World Model 的「最后一公里」，</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"10\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">卡在 Web 端渲染</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"11\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比 Genie3 等视频生成范式的世界模型，其对算力的依赖极为庞大，距离在 Web 端实现高质量、实时运行仍有不小差距。反观神经渲染路线，尤其是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;3D Gaussian Splatting</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，凭借其高效性，已经成为构建世界模型的重要表示形式。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"11\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3DGS 让高质量、实时的 3D 世界成为可能，但在实际落地中，仍存在明显断层：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">桌面端 / 引擎方案（SIBR、Unity、Unreal）：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">性能强，但依赖沉重、部署复杂，难以传播与复现；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">现有 Web 端方案（SparkJS、SuperSplat）：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">受限于 WebGL 管线，主要支持静态或预计算高斯，难以承载实时推理的动态 3DGS、Neural Avatar，更难引入生成式模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"13\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">World Model 想要真正「被看见、被交互」，Web 端渲染底座成为关键瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"14\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Visionary：不是 Viewer，</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"14\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">而是 World Model 的 Web 渲染基座</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"15\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Visionary 的定位并非「又一个 3DGS 查看器」，而是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">一个面向 World Model / 空间智能的 Web 原生渲染基座 (Rendering Substrate)</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">WebGPU 原生架构：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将 GPU 计算与渲染真正带入浏览器，替代 WebGL；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">ONNX 驱动的统一接口：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将「每帧高斯生成 / 更新」抽象为标准化的模型契约；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">动态友好设计：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3DGS、4DGS、Neural Avatar 以及生成式后处理均可在线运行。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"18\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Visionary 的核心设计在于提出了 Gaussian Generator Contract：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524327\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3055555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee267c67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibMWHN2gz8SLUucnTjmv5AohQPadxRfLvQFTT78xF4IANP2ylMMq92ORibIXUEiaeRGZuGOybNO5p7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将各类 3DGS、4DGS 及 Avatar 方法统一导出为 ONNX 标准，每帧仅需输入相机、时间等轻量控制信号，即可由 ONNX 输出完整的高斯属性缓冲。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"19,0,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种设计使得渲染器不再受限于具体的算法细节，首次在浏览器端实现了每帧动态生成与更新高斯、同一渲染器承载多种 3DGS 变体以及接入生成式后处理（如风格化、增强）的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"22\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">性能实测：</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"22\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">全面超越 SparkJS</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524320\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2873ec60&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibMWHN2gz8SLUucnTjmv5AopUl5Xy61LpiaeYQSB5sodlLekf1bicaJvxiaHCujjj2hIKBianUOrvkCpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"23\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实验数据显示，在相同 3DGS 资源条件下，Visionary 的渲染效率显著优于当前主流 Web 端查看器。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"24\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在包含数百万高斯点的典型场景中，Visionary 将排序与预处理完全迁移至 GPU (WebGPU)，显著降低端到端延迟，而 SparkJS 的性能瓶颈主要集中在 CPU 排序阶段。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><font face=\"等线 Light\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">不止更快：</span></span></font></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><font face=\"等线 Light\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">渲染正确性与画质同样重要</span></span></font></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524321\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6ab2fabc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibMWHN2gz8SLUucnTjmv5AoicaqkQ6icLopfT2oS12X7ib3hBW8iby5KAV3tFGYxxlD6VyqprNepDlgtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"27,0,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Visionary 采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">逐帧 GPU 全局排序</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，彻底避免了类似 SparkJS 在快速视角变化下出现的 lazy sorting 视觉伪影。在 Mip-NeRF360 等基准上，画质指标与 SparkJS 持平甚至略有提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"27,1,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时避免了 SuperSplat 等方案中的逐物体排序混合错误。在多模型混合场景下，仍能保证透明度渲染正确。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"28\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">面向研究、创作与工业的统一平台</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524322\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a519a54&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibMWHN2gz8SLUucnTjmv5AoU7x7KgxDUrDeHPrzQcWPEpKsriasL8IzHibDX0XtdKkqhdiazRYok1Viaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">对研究者来说，任意</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;3DGS&nbsp;</span></span><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">变体只要能导出</span></span></font><font face=\"Aptos\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ONNX</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，即可快速复现、对比与展示；创作者无需安装专业软件，即可在浏览器中完成编辑、录制与渲染；</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">工业界则可将其应用于数字孪生、仿真、</span></span></font><font face=\"Aptos\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">XR</span></span></font><font face=\"等线\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">、具身智能等大规模实时场景。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"31\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Visionary 已在 GitHub 完全开源，采用宽松协议，并已获得 Firefox / Chrome WebGPU 相关开发者的关注与反馈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524319\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.583596214511041\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"951\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4af3eb79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWibMWHN2gz8SLUucnTjmv5AoRPf0AtVervic7XjA7BaRB7g6gVO6sKKiam1bYYv4Be43ndQStCibBnuqw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"32\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前已原生支持：MLP-based 3DGS (Scaffold-GS)、4D Gaussian Splatting、Neural Avatar (LHM、GauHuman、R³-Avatar 等)、ONNX 生成式后处理（风格化、增强），全部渲染流程均在浏览器端完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"35\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">团队表示，Visionary 只是迈向统一世界模型框架的第一步。未来将进一步探索：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"36,0,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">物理交互增强</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（碰撞检测与 Mesh 管线融合）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"36,1,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">物理感知建模</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（结合 MPM 等方法模拟真实动力学）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"36,2,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">空间智能体</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（基于多模态大模型的空间推理与交互）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-path-to-node=\"36,3,0\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"36,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">下游应用桥接</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（支持具身 AI 的 Sim-to-Real 迁移）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3 data-path-to-node=\"37\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">结语</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"38\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">World Model 的竞争，最终会回到一个问题：谁能把复杂世界，稳定、快速、低门槛地呈现出来？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"40\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Visionary 给出的答案是：用 WebGPU + ONNX，把世界模型真正带到 Web。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Visionary 是一个基于 WebGPU 和 ONNX 的 Web 渲染平台，专为世界模型和空间智能设计，通过将 3DGS/4DGS 实时渲染带入浏览器，解决了现有 Web 端渲染器的性能瓶颈和功能限制，并全面超越了基于 WebGL 的 SparkJS。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Visionary 是一个基于 WebGPU 和 ONNX 的 Web 渲染平台，专为世界模型和空间智能设计，通过将 3DGS/4DGS 实时渲染带入浏览器，解决了现有 Web 端渲染器的性能瓶颈和功能限制，并全面超越了基于 WebGL 的 SparkJS。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了开源项目 Visionary，该项目旨在解决世界模型在 Web 端可视化与交互中面临的渲染瓶颈。针对现有基于 WebGL 的方案（如 SparkJS）在处理动态场景、复杂场景以及生成模型时的性能和功能限制，Visionary 提出了一种基于 WebGPU 和 ONNX 的全新渲染基座。其核心创新在于通过 Gaussian Generator Contract 将各类高斯模型统一导出为 ONNX 标准，首次在浏览器端实现了每帧动态生成与更新高斯，并支持多种 3DGS 变体和生成式后处理。实验数据显示，Visionary 在性能上显著优于 SparkJS，并将排序与预处理完全迁移至 GPU，有效避免了视觉伪影。此外，Visionary 还具备面向研究、创作与工业的统一平台潜力，已实现对多种 Neural Avatar 和 ONNX 生成式后处理的原生支持。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "现有 Web 端世界模型渲染面临底层能力瓶颈。",
      "explanation": "传统基于 WebGL 的渲染器（如 SparkJS）在大场景、复杂动态场景下存在 CPU 排序性能瓶颈，难以支持动态 3DGS 和生成模型，阻碍了世界模型的可视化与交互。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Visionary 通过 WebGPU 和 ONNX 构建 Web 原生渲染基座，全面超越现有方案。",
      "explanation": "Visionary 利用 WebGPU 将 GPU 计算与渲染引入浏览器，并结合 ONNX 统一高斯生成接口，实现了真正的动态实时渲染，解决了性能和功能限制，显著优于 SparkJS。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Gaussian Generator Contract 是 Visionary 的核心创新，实现高斯模型的动态生成与更新。",
      "explanation": "该契约将各类 3DGS/4DGS 等方法统一为 ONNX 标准，使得渲染器能动态生成和更新高斯，支持多种 3DGS 变体和生成式后处理，极大提升了灵活性和应用潜力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Visionary 实现了渲染性能和画质的显著提升，避免视觉伪影。",
      "explanation": "通过将排序和预处理完全迁移至 GPU，Visionary 显著降低了端到端延迟，并采用逐帧 GPU 全局排序，有效避免了快速视角变化下的视觉伪影，保证了渲染正确性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "世界模型的可视化与交互，依然严重受限于底层 Web 端渲染能力。",
    "Visionary 的定位并非「又一个 3DGS 查看器」，而是一个面向 World Model / 空间智能的 Web 原生渲染基座 (Rendering Substrate)。",
    "实验数据显示，在相同 3DGS 资源条件下，Visionary 的渲染效率显著优于当前主流 Web 端查看器。",
